field_not_aggregatable.text: Detector field "{{fieldName}}" is not an aggregatable field.

fields_not_aggregatable.text: One of the detector fields is not an aggregatable field.

cardinality_by_field.text: Cardinality of by_field "{{fieldName}}" is above 1000 and might result in high memory usage.

cardinality_over_field_low.text: Cardinality of over_field "{{fieldName}}" is below 10 and might be less suitable for population analysis.

cardinality_over_field_high.text: Cardinality of over_field "{{fieldName}}" is above 1000000 and might result in high memory usage.

cardinality_partition_field.text: Cardinality of partition_field "{{fieldName}}" is above 1000 and might result in high memory usage.

cardinality_model_plot_high.text: The estimated cardinality of {{modelPlotCardinality}} of fields relevant to creating model plots might result in resource intensive jobs.

bucket_span_empty.text: The bucket span field must be specified.

bucket_span_estimation_mismatch.text: Current bucket span is "{{currentBucketSpan}}", but bucket span estimation returned "{{estimateBucketSpan}}".

bucket_span_high.text: Bucket span is 1 day or more. Be aware that days are considered as UTC days, not local days.

bucket_span_invalid.text: The specified bucket span is not a valid time interval format e.g. 10m, 1h. It also needs to be higher than zero.

detectors_duplicates.text: Duplicate detectors were found. Detectors having the same combined configuration for 'function', 'field_name', 'by_field_name', 'over_field_name' and 'partition_field_name' are not allowed within the same job.

detectors_empty.text: No detectors were found. At least one detector must be specified.

detectors_function_empty.text: One of the detector functions is empty.

index_fields_invalid.text: Could not load fields from index.

influencer_high.text: The job configuration includes more than 3 influencers. Consider using fewer influencers or creating multiple jobs.

influencer_low.text: No influencers have been configured. Picking an influencer is strongly recommended.

influencer_low_suggestion.text: No influencers have been configured. Consider using {{influencerSuggestion}} as an influencer.

influencer_low_suggestions.text: No influencers have been configured. Consider using one or more of {{influencerSuggestion}}.

job_id_empty.text: The job name field must not be empty.

job_id_invalid.text: The job name is invalid. It can contain lowercase alphanumeric (a-z and 0-9) characters, hyphens or underscores and must start and end with an alphanumeric character.

job_group_id_invalid.text: One of the job group names is invalid. They can contain lowercase alphanumeric (a-z and 0-9) characters, hyphens or underscores and must start and end with an alphanumeric character.

skipped_extended_tests.text: Skipped some checks because the basic requirements of the job configuration were not met.

estimated_mml_greater_than_max_mml.text: The estimated model memory limit is greater than the max model memory limit configured for this cluster.

mml_greater_than_max_mml.text: The model memory limit is greater than the max model memory limit configured for this cluster.

mml_value_invalid.text: {{mml}} is not a valid value for model memory limit. The value should be specified in bytes e.g. 10MB

estimated_mml_greater_than_mml.text: The estimated model memory limit is greater than the model memory limit you have configured.

time_field_invalid.text: '{{timeField}}' cannot be used as the time-field because it's not a valid field of type 'date'.

time_range_short.text: The selected or available time range might be too short. The recommended minimum time range should be at least {{minTimeSpanReadable}} and {{bucketSpanCompareFactor}} times the bucket span.

time_range_before_epoch.text: The selected or available time range contains data with timestamps before the UNIX epoch beginning. Timestamps before 01/01/1970 00:00:00 (UTC) are not supported for machine learning jobs.
